to look behind me ♪

41:18.693 --> 41:20.956
I could set up a satellite lab
in Seattle.

41:21.000 --> 41:23.785
I could travel back and forth
once a week.

41:23.829 --> 41:26.527
That's the best
I can offer.

41:26.571 --> 41:28.398
♪ I'm awake

41:28.442 --> 41:30.096
Done.

